<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454261>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–20. Female Lamprima species, dorsal view: 15, L. adolphinae (Gestro, 1875); 16, L. aenea (Fabricius, 1792); 17, L. aurata Latreille, 1804, Sydney, New South Wales; 18, L. aurata, Sydney, New South Wales, blue form; 19, L. aurata, Western Australia; 20, L. insularis W.J. Macleay, 1885." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454261/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454273>
    dc:description "FIGURES 54–57. Male Lamprima species, elytral disc microsculpture, at low and high magnification: 54–55, L. adolphinae (Gestro, 1875); 56–57, L. aurata Latreille, 1804. Large punctures approximately 25 microns in diameter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454273/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454275>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58–61. Lamprima aurata Latreille, 1804, lateral view of mesoventrite process: 58, male, northern Queensland; 59, female, northern Queensland; 60, male, Victoria; 61, female, Victoria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454275/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454287>
    dc:description "FIGURES 89–94. Lamprima species, ovipositor and spermatheca: 89, L. adolphinae (Gestro, 1875); 90, L. aenea (Fabricius, 1792); 91, L. aurata Latreille, 1804 (Bridport, Tasmania); Lamprima species, spermathecae: 92, L. aurata (Ourimbah, central New South Wales); 93, L. aurata (Nadgee, south New South Wales); 94, L. insularis W.J. Macleay, 1885." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454287/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1454289>
    dc:description "FIGURES 95–96. 95, Map of Australia and New Guinea to show Lamprima species: O= L. adolphinae (Gestro, 1875), Ɨ= L. aurata Latreille, 1804. 96, Map of Lord Howe to show distribution of Lamprima insularis W.J. Macleay, 1885 (shaded area = 500 + m)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1454289/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

